Elizar Perla is a recently retired
cat burglar who has succumbed to the temptation of
one final score. The target is David Gray, famous
for his collection of art and other rarities. Soon
after the job, Elizar disappears, leaving his
daughter Marty distraught. Desperate, Gray
approaches Marty suggesting that her father will
turn up as soon as the stolen artwork is recovered.
She begrudgingly accepts the offer to help him
locate the art, but all is not as it seems, as the
rarest of stolen pieces has value beyond ordinary currency
